				<div class="bookname">
					<h1> 第81章</h1>
					<div class="bottem1">
						<a href="javascript:;" onclick="showpop('/modules/article/uservote.php?id=51741&amp;ajax_request=1');">投推荐票</a> <a href="/51_51741/19690307.html">上一章</a> ← <a href="http://www.benbenwx.com/51_51741/">章节目录</a> → <a href="/51_51741/19690310.html">下一章</a> <a href="javascript:;" onclick="showpop('/modules/article/addbookcase.php?id=51741&amp;cid=19690308&amp;ajax_request=1');">加入书签</a>
